@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nnnadh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.abs(v2 + 0.14) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.09)))
    v1 = ((v0 / (v1 + 0.26 * v2 + 0.91)) + (wp.sin(v1 + 0.06) * (v1 + 0.14 - tmp + 0.61)))
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v0 + 0.61 + tmp + 0.24)))
    v0 = 0.29
    tmp = (tmp / wp.abs((v1 + 0.14 * v1 + 0.37)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.90)) - (v1 - (v1 + 0.55 / tmp + 0.40)))
    v2 = 0.34
    data[tid] = v0
